replies.body:
The issue is, most of the typical "axe wielding maniac" playstyles have already been taken.

Berserker who refuses to die? {{champion:2}} 

Throws axes to inflict massive damage {{champion:119}} 


Swings a giant axe around  and overpowers opponent {{champion:122}} 

The only thing I could think of is a valkyre sort of character, who will keep spinning around an axe while being flying around a battlefield, but that is taken by {{champion:86}} and {{champion:55}}  as league's fidget spinner.
